"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-09-03-Chinese-Olympic-champions-bring-joy-to-residents-in-Macao-SAR-1wB98mRqYta-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  Chinese mainland Olympians visited three community service centers and engaged with residents in the Macao Special Administrative Region (SAR) on the morning\\u00a0of September 2 as part of their three-day visit. Since the conclusion of the Sydney Olympic Games in 2000, it has been a tradition for mainland Olympians to visit Macao, immersing themselves in local social service organizations.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"